{"tid":1045602,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[搵笨]富士夢想航空訪日外國人國內線優惠","createTime":"2019-03-03T16:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:19:25.000Z","uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8ce1e15067333b7022ec64d378833dd684f491","tid":1045602,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"呢間野相信香港人比較陌生<br />\n見近來唔少人打算攻略日本比較冷門地方<br />\n分享下呢個優惠 不過不如搭ana<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fujidream.co.jp/company/press/doc/190228.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujidream.co.jp%2Fcompany%2Fpress%2Fdoc%2F190228.pdf&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=210cc6c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fujidream.co.jp/company/press/doc/190228.pdf</a><br />\n只限訪日外國人 姐係長居個班無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到機場check in,要show護照同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">前往日本以及離開日本既國際線機票</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我日文唔好 唔肯定係咪一定要機票<br />\n可能print張email出黎都過到骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且佢官網無得買 要去ctrip/eDream/Qunar等機票網<br />\n<br />\n香港出發可以考慮福岡/名古屋轉機<br />\n尤其福岡機場係世界上同市區最近既機場之一<br />\n相信非常適合玩盡兩個地方<br />\n有咩路線就呢度搵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fujidream.co.jp/sp/timetable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujidream.co.jp%2Fsp%2Ftimetable%2F&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=f64b1edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fujidream.co.jp/sp/timetable/</a><br />\n<br />\n利申非打手 如果一定要show回程機票<br />\n可以顯示出日本人個腦幾咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9520569a81358dc3c4e878d504252d93cdd3ae","tid":1045602,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"可能對飛機膠係好消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fujidream.co.jp/sp/flight/kizai.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujidream.co.jp%2Fsp%2Fflight%2Fkizai.html&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=d3c219de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fujidream.co.jp/sp/flight/kizai.html</a>"},{"pid":"458d4d3119109856de609e65638fb406025f12a3","tid":1045602,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n人地擺明居馬吸引外國遊客"},{"pid":"df5e29676506030b58de27b63a1bc81a081ca431","tid":1045602,"uid":8203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"458d4d3119109856de609e65638fb406025f12a3","tid":1045602,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n人地擺明居馬吸引外國遊客"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"點樣比到張回程機票佢睇？"},{"pid":"d2aebfee4543bc8a8506f6a5618815443d150c42","tid":1045602,"uid":8435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"df5e29676506030b58de27b63a1bc81a081ca431","tid":1045602,"uid":8203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"458d4d3119109856de609e65638fb406025f12a3","tid":1045602,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n人地擺明居馬吸引外國遊客"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"點樣比到張回程機票佢睇？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"其實人哋有寫e-ticket<br />\n就算呢個年代仲有人用紙機票，咁更加拎得出<br />\n<br />\n定係你係咪以為機票=boarding pass?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0d350bb23fe31021e00bb7cd8439d326858e2d","tid":1045602,"uid":33703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:08:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎 我坐呢間不如坐jal ana 仲有得儲下里數 仲有多啲班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1961c98a97ab1d4fe1617dc554506cc4fe83e9ec","tid":1045602,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:08:58.000Z","ms